13.19 m. to the point of

beginning; containing an area of Five Hundred Forty-Two Square Meters and Thirty-Five Sq. Decimeters (542.35) . All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground by PS cyl. Conc. Mons. except points 4,5, and 1 by Old PLS. cyl. conc. mons. bearings true; date of the original survey, Dec. 1910-June 1911 and that of the subdn. survey, March 23, 1982. Approved on July 7, 1982.

Lot 4, Blk. 464 TCT No. 50664

A parcel of land (Lot 4 Blk. 464 of the subd. plan Psd-55322 being a portion of Blk. No. 502 of plan Psd-52256 LRC GLRO Rec. No. 7681), situated in Q. City, Is. of Luzon. Bounded on the NE., along line 1-2-3 by St. Lot 15 of the subd. plan; on the SE., along line 3-4 by Lot 6 BIk. 464 of the subd. Plan; on the SW., along line 4-5 by Lot 3 BIk. 464 of the subd. plan; & on the NW., along line 5-1 by Lot 2 BIk. 464 of the subd. plan. Beginning at a point marked “1” on plan, being N. 78 deg. 05’E., 2360.00 m. from CBM No. 17, Manila Cad.;

beginning; containing an area of One Thousand Eighty Four Square Meters and 90/100 decimeters (1,084.90) . All prs. referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground by PLS Cyl. Conc. Mons. 15 x 60 cm., bearings true; date of the original survey Dec. 1910 – June 1911 & that of the subd. survey Sept. 9 – Oct. 12, 1957 & Oct. 6 – Dec. 15, 1958 & date of approval Mar. 24, 1959.

IN WITNESS THEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed hereto.

Done in the City of Manila, this 4th day of August , in the year of our Lord, Two Thousand and Six.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) EDUARDO R. ERMITA Executive Secretary

